# Trivy CVE allowlist for the MLSS repo.
#
# Format: one CVE per line.
#   CVE-XXXX-YYYY    # short reason — review date YYYY-MM
#
# Trivy ignores any CVE listed here when computing the severity
# gate in .gitea/workflows/trivy.yml. Each entry needs a comment
# explaining WHY (transitive dep we can't bump, accepted risk,
# false positive, etc.) plus a review date so we know when to
# reassess (target: every 6 months, or when the underlying dep
# bumps).
#
# Currently empty — populate when a real finding needs an
# exception. Adding lines here without justification defeats
# the security gate.
